edu.wisc.trace.uch.util.socket

Class UISocketCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wisc.trace.uch.util.socket.AbstractUISocketElement
      • edu.wisc.trace.uch.util.socket.UISocketCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUISocketElement
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UISocketBasicCommand, UISocketTimedCommand, UISocketVoidCommand

    public abstract class UISocketCommand
extends AbstractUISocketElement
    UISocketCommand is the command variant of UISocketElement. It also serves as the base class for all of the specific command types.
    Version:
    $Revision: 798 $
    Author:
    Parikshit Thakur & Team, Trace R&D Center
